Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.62,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.63,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.91,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備好用飛彈\N攻擊殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.75,0:01:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還能戰鬥吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務，明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.41,0:02:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十一話\N[幸福的去向]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.89,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒備這麼森嚴不能動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，就算想搶奪運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.27,0:02:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要過了沙漠才有機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.45,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，那麼多警戒機飛來飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也不能動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過一會會有大風沙吹來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.43,0:02:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候我們就橫越這沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起來好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了，現在一起行動比較安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.74,0:03:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想收拾心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能收集的已盡量收集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但重要的部份幾乎已被破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是，所以才要自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.59,0:03:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈變成這樣子只是一堆廢鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，是一堆鋼彈合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.76,0:03:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是托爾吉斯的後繼機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它基本上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該運用了托爾吉斯的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵，可以把這部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.34,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運去維多利亞基地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要修理它嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.52,0:03:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或許執著於那駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的駕駛員死了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那爆炸中的確沒理由能生還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我希望他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個必須互相駕駛機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決一勝負的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起!特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擅作主張直接攻擊殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了那些鋼彈是一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有異常攻擊力的人造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.02,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要打倒的是鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，支援者的活動令人擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宇宙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想避免敵人的勢力再擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託妳了，蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!\N我會撤底消滅他們給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星裡主張和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會討厭軍事介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後要抑制無禮的招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就從莫斯科升空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那城市住了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.05,0:05:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能了解OZ尊貴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們會協助妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,周圍雷達沒反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!那最不可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散開戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是看見風沙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種地方有甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.88,0:05:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不屬於地球圈統一聯合和OZ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中東諸國的軍事基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們躲在那城裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地底基地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是我們[馬格亞那部隊]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所屬國家的基地\N你們的國家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎你來，卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久違了，沙達吾爾令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.23,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落地球後的任務很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，這裡的馬格亞那隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.56,0:06:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫了我很多，我經常麻煩他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.07,0:06:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能幫到你，我們樂意效勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就能給OZ多一點損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然拿衛星作擋箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是人類的所為!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能阻止他們是我們的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，是我們的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.95,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，無人怪責你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們留下來整備機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你們，拉席得，還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，兩部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都會好好整備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題，拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫卡特爾‧拉巴伯‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你就是阿拉伯諸國裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有有數發言權和財力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿家的繼承人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我也明白為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這種地方會有勢力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿家主張和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在走了出來\N等於被逐出家門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多內情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫迪歐，迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會逃跑也會躲藏，但不說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.55,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞衛星派了\N機動戰士來地面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確有數部機動戰士\N被派到地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.72,0:07:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且進行了各種破壞行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，OZ為了地球的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經開始了\N消滅叛亂份子的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,判亂被平息\N也只是時間的問題…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.47,0:08:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一點也不襯玫瑰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，妳有請帖嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.67,0:08:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，今日的派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有受邀請的人才能參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，妳有朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜，妳來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偉列茲公爵大人，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道她是公爵大人的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去吧，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派對開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡只有老人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這種年輕人很少見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偉列茲公爵，你的舞伴真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.14,0:09:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.21,0:09:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以和我跳隻舞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我要第一個和她跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果妳不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以和我跳隻舞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎會介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你不嫌棄我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正門入口戒備就位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.90,0:09:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後門現在正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上空雷達沒反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，繼續戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.34,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳果然有匹斯克拉福特家有風采
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識匹斯克拉福特家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和山克王國的王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特家交情甚深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.79,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直至13年前王族滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.37,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何匹斯克拉福特王族會滅亡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有渴望和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.57,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就有想從戰爭中得到利益的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前者是匹斯克拉福特家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後者就是地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.05,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即提倡和平卻被當成障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連否定聯合的羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也開始了使用武力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼是OZ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想問特列斯他有何打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以叫他來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他竟然叫代理人來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼，別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偉列茲公爵在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是特列斯大人的代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和他打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍服不襯攻瑰花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像莉莉娜妳般善良的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才襯得起攻瑰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偉列茲公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是特列斯‧克修里那達的代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和你單獨會談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.10,0:11:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先\N可以給我那朵玫瑰花嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想送給我的孫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧德利安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳為何會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.91,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺，我也襯不起攻瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.02,0:11:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ敗類的血才襯我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要替爸爸報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公爵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.14,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能做的只有擋在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.44,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不及那個女孩般勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家是那個女孩的擁護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出去追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.55,0:12:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,須要那個女孩剛才的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要向她學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒異常吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,節日嗎?好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慶祝我們馬格亞那隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.42,0:12:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,40部機平安歸來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這國家一直反抗聯合軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠自己的力量自衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.59,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬格亞那隊是他們的先鋒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先鋒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.74,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別推我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不塊是先鋒，是這國家的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一條心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這國家的快樂全因那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.11,0:13:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥到底的心令一個國家團結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很多事想談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以，我才要拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡只有我們兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有5部?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在新愛德華出現的5部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我由衛星來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.91,0:13:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們5人，機動戰士和行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有消滅OZ的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ搞亂了衛星的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記著那任務一直戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.39,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候，我收到那部機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活著一日就要作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被OZ統治，我寧願死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我抱著那決心作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…不能死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛做了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星無心戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能犧牲衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.39,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的朋友好完美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.12,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我希望他多照顧自己一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈一行動衛星就會被攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我們明知會那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.10,0:14:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家並非一條心的戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒人比孤獨的士兵更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請馬上到司令室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ機動戰士部隊接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉席得，看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偵察隊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎辦?拉席得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡戰鬥會牽連國民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續戒備，士兵在地底候命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是某種節日嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為友國的朋友來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的部隊休息和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以給我們少許糧食和水嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能的範圍內可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，戒備得好森嚴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.51,0:15:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情報說中東的叛軍\N躲藏在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要非常謹慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那東西是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，OZ走了，調查那東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.94,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少許震動也會令它爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉席得，甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的傢伙假裝休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.25,0:16:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這城市裝了廿多個炸彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.46,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計時炸彈的話，回收丟掉就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像設計成不能移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換言之\N他們是要毀滅這城市…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.53,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要逼出馬格亞那隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈定在深夜12時爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們看來想在夜間進行沙漠戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.11,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即他們準備了夜間戰的裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者是叫我們在12時前投降呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈連累了你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯!我們被跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的攻擊方法很周詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.92,0:16:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從以前起\N這城市已經被懷疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ已經被發現這裡並會進行攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.70,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經不能再瞞騙他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我們要一面集中攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人包圍網的一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面讓平民離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，還有一項光榮的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是讓兩部鋼彈平安脫險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈是為了打倒OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而出現在這地球的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ卑鄙的戰略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令他們不能參加這次戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.35,0:17:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N鋼彈終有一日會拯救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能先向他們報恩\N是我們的光榮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白嗎?兄弟們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全軍出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.68,0:17:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中東軍的氣墊型開始攻擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各隊馬上還擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人氣墊型的速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉為接近戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向敵人的地底出口開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.76,0:18:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有很多出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!在北面出口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人運輸機任我們挑選!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，馬上佔領它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.84,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別慌張，大家去北面出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別離開大隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.75,0:18:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們和北面出口\N的亞布度會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是麻煩你們卻幫不到忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.13,0:19:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒用!可恨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.53,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈是英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能並肩作戰的日子一定會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向那束花發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.02,0:19:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終有一日迎戰的日子一定來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是艾達，誘敵作戰完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退到山裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓平民受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.73,0:19:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則馬格亞那會名譽掃地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護卡特爾少爺\N運輸機的航路!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.55,0:20:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬格亞那隊全面集結!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別降低彈幕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.13,0:20:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以在空中旋轉一圈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然甚麼也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想…幫點忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.64,0:20:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕!冷靜應戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.29,0:20:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬格亞那隊全體後退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.47,0:20:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見，馬格亞那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次見面時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.98,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會和衛星一條心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在這裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這ㄚ頭真大膽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩交給我看管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是蕾蒂‧安特校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.77,0:21:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能服從特尉妳的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你那麼想要原因…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得到特列斯大人的批準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那行了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們冒犯妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.06,0:21:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的氣質和某人很相似吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.93,0:21:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也是OZ的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.41,0:22:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來接妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.38,0:22:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.75,0:22:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.00,0:22:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.00,0:22:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.00,0:22:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.00,0:22:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.50,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.00,0:23:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.50,0:23:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.00,0:23:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.00,0:23:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了贏得和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得不拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在充滿矛盾的戰場上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.83,0:23:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛遇上莎莉‧普奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛說他只可和弱者戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.14,0:23:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉感到那句話中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.71,0:23:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰士無處宣洩的憤恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.14,0:23:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然迷失於自己的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.81,0:23:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但五飛再次駕駛神龍鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.32,0:23:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰士-鋼彈W，第十二話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.49,0:23:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷惑的戰士們

